#: constants/HelpData.ts:129
msgid "Tap Sign In With Google in Settings to connect your account. Signing in enables cloud backups so your data is safe if you switch devices or reinstall the app, and your name is shown in the home screen greeting. The app works fully offline without signing in, but cloud backups are unavailable. Your data is stored locally on your device and is not shared with anyone unless you choose to share it yourself."
